details.description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low White ‘07 features an all-white leather upper with a perforated toe box and Swoosh overlays. A Nike heel embroidery and white sole completes the design.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Supreme Black

details.description:
Supreme and Nike paid homage to an NYC classic with the release of the Nike Air Force 1 Low Supreme Black, now available on StockX. This collaboration adds Supreme’s world-renowned Box Logo to the side of a traditional all-black Air Force 1 design.

This Air Force 1 Low is comprised of an all-black leather upper with matching soles and detailing. A red Supreme Box Logo placed on the outside heel completes the design. These sneakers released in March of 2020 and retailed for $118.

details.description:
The women's Nike Air Force 1 Low White silhouette (W) continues the tradition of the 1982 Air Force 1. The sneaker features an all-white leather upper with a perforated toe box and Swoosh overlays. A Nike heel embroidery and white sole completes the design.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Black

details.description:
The all-black Air Force 1 Low is a timeless classic in Nike's catalog of heritage sneakers.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 Black features a triple black smooth leather upper with a matching Air sole and laces. Subtle Nike Air embroidery on the heel tab nods to the history of the AF-1 line. A metallic lace tag and woven tongue label complete the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 retails for $115.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Lil Yachty Concrete Boys Lucky Green
Nike Air Force 1 Low Drake NOCTA Certified Lover Boy

details.description:
Previously dubbed "Certified Lover Boy", the new premium Drake-inspired AF1 is now known as the "Love You Forever." This sentiment is inspired by Drake’s favorite childhood book with subtle added details of the scripted "Love You Forever" on the midsole, in the same white color. Additional design elements include customized laces, NOCTA logo on left heel, and a new perforation pattern on toe box.
​
The special-edition Drake Nike Air Force 1 Low released December of 2022 for $160.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Off-White Varsity Maize

details.description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Off White Varsity Maize represents a collaboration between Nike and Virgil Abloh’s fashion house Off-White. This sneaker takes an iconic silhouette and a retro colorway and infuses it with hallmark Off-White creativity.​
​​
​The Off White X Nike Air Force 1 Mid-Top Varsity Maize SP sports an upper with a base of tumbled white leather and perforations in the toe box. The overlays and ankle strap are maize-colored tumbled leather, while the side-panel Nike swoosh is white tumbled leather. The laces are maize and an extra pair of white laces threads through fly cables on the upper. The white foam midsole houses visible Air and sits atop a maize rubber outsole where the classic AF1 traction pattern has been enhanced with track spikes.​
​​
​What we love most about this creative shoe is the Off-White branding. Characteristic Off-White text appears on the medial upper while a white grim reaper graphic is embroidered on the lateral heel. The Nike Air Force 1 Mid SP Off White Varsity Maze was released on November 9, 2023, for a retail price of $205.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low Mushroom (Women's)

details.description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low Mushroom (Women's), in women’s sizes, is a sneaker with a Sail leather upper, overlaid by Pink Foam and Elemental Pink nubuck leather at the tip, lace panel, and heel. The tongue and Nike Swoosh are done in Pink Foam woven fabric, and a wooden hang tag displays a Nike Swoosh branded mushroom character. Multi-colored mushroom characters and motifs are embroidered on the vamp, heel, and cork insole, while Nike branding appears on the heel tab and tongue.

American athletic wear brand Nike debuted the Air Force 1 in 1982, and it remains one of Nike’s most popular styles over forty years later. Keeping fans on their toes, Nike introduced mascots for Spring 2025, inspired by forest wildlife. The mushroom characters’ AF1 appearance is their second, following the their debut on the Air Jordan 1 Low.

Our experts feel that the best feature of the Air Force 1 Mushroom is its fungi-themed accents, which are a cute and rare styling of the shoe. The Nike Air Force 1 Low Mushroom (Women's) released on March 1, 2025, and retailed for $135.

Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White (GS)

details.description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White GS  features triple white leather upper perforations on the toebox as well as two perforations under each Swoosh. The Swoosh and overlays are also white leather. The outsole is white with a concentric-circles pattern and stars in the rubber. The midsole is white with a hidden Air compartment. The midsole says "AIR" in white. A silver tab saying "AF1" is on the top of the white laces.

This grade school-sized shoe, the Nike Air Force 1 Low LE Triple White GS, was released on April 13, 2021 at a retail price of $90.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Flyknit 2 White Pure Platinum

details.description:
The Nike Air Force 1 Flyknit 2 White Pure Platinum features a white and Pure Platinum Flyknit and nubuck upper. From there, nubuck on the eyestays and logo and "Ultra" construction on the white midsole complete the design.

The Nike Air Force 1 Flyknit 2 White Pure Platinum released in May of 2019 and retailed for $110.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 LV8 Black Gum Light Brown White
Nike Air Force 1 Low G-Dragon Peaceminusone Para-Noise 3.0

details.description:
Disclaimer: Please be aware of paint fragility regarding the first layer of color on the upper. Due to the thin coating of paint, colors may rub off.

Introducing the Nike Air Force 1 Low G-Dragon Peaceminusone Para-Noise 3.0, the third installment in the highly coveted collaboration between Nike and South Korean artist G-Dragon utilizing the Air Force 1 base. This special edition features a black leather upper that wears away over time to reveal hidden artwork by G-Dragon, adding a personal, creative touch to every pair. The sneaker showcases contrasting swooshes in yellow, pink, and blue, with a signature sunflower logo on the tongue and custom graphics on the insoles, giving this sneaker a vibrant and artistic vibe.

In keeping with the Air Force 1’s legendary status in both basketball and streetwear, the Para-Noise 3.0 incorporates G-Dragon’s unique artistic flair with features like brushstrokes along the midsole, custom pins, and a special-edition box. Since its debut in 1982, the Air Force 1 has evolved into one of the most iconic sneakers in Nike’s lineup, and this collaboration adds yet another layer of creativity to its storied history.

Released on September 14, 2024, the Nike Air Force 1 Low G-Dragon Peaceminusone Para-Noise 3.0 retailed at $200. The black, new emerald, pinkfire, tour yellow, and blue gale colorway, paired with G-Dragon’s signature artwork, makes this release a statement piece for both sneakerheads and art enthusiasts alike. This collaboration continues to redefine what a sneaker can be—a canvas for both fashion and expression.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid Off-White Pine Green

details.description:
Off-White and Nike are partnering together again on another Air Force 1 sneaker collaboration, with the release of the Nike Air Force 1 Mid Off-White Pine Green.

Nike’s Air Force 1 Mid Off-White Pine Green is constructed using green premium leather throughout the body of the sneaker. Nike used white accents, the sneakers branding, zip tie, Swooshes, and midsole. The sneakers draw inspiration from Track and Field shoes with a spike like design on the outsoles.

The Nike Air Force 1 Mid Off-White Pine Green released April 28, 2023, with a retail price of $205.

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low '07 White Swoosh Panda

details.description: The Nike Air Force 1 07 Low White Swoosh Panda is a stylish and versatile sneaker that combines classic design with modern features. The shoe features a white leather upper with black accents and a panda graphic on the heel. The iconic Nike Swoosh is also featured in white on the sides. The shoe is made with high-quality materials, including a durable rubber sole and a comfortable foam midsole. The release date for this shoe is January 31, 2023, and with a retail price of $130. Whether you're looking for a casual everyday shoe or a stylish addition to your sneaker collection, the Nike Air Force 1 07 Low White Swoosh Panda is a great choice.
